<author>mynạ mkrm, rạjy kmạl</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wḥdk mạ byn ạlnạs ậmnt yạ dymạs
 bạ̹lhk ạlḥnwn fạdy kl ạlạ̉jnạs
 wḥdk byn ạljmwʿ ṣrkẖt bṣwt ʿẓym
 ạdẖkrny yạ yswʿ fy mlkwt ạlnʿym
 ạlsạʿẗ ạltạsʿẗ sẖạhdẗ ʿly̱ ạlḥb ạlkbyr
 tḥky lynạ ṭhạrtk wnhạytk fy ạlmsyr
 wḥdk mʿạk hnqwl wnṣrkẖ bṣwt ʿẓym
 ạdẖkrnạ yạ yswʿ fy mlkwt ạlnʿym
 ạdẖkrnạ yạ ạ̹lhnạ fy nhạyẗ ạlzmạn ạgẖfr lynạ
 ạlkẖṭạyạ
 ḥqq lynạ ạlạ̉mạn wqlwbnạ lyk mrfwʿẗ ttrk
 lynạ ạlzmạn</lyrics>
<title>dymạs</title>
</song>